subject: Football (College)
Bowl Games
lead_paragraph: Michael Frisina came up big for Boise State, kicking a 27-yard field goal with 1 minute 16 seconds left to give the No. 20 Broncos their third straight Las Vegas Bowl win, a 28-26 victory over Washington.
